  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The hypothesis of the present study is that an automatic assessment technic can measure the
      impact of the speech disorders on the communication abilities giving a severity index of
      speech in patients treated for head and neck and particularly for oral and pharyngeal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
