  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>carcinologic speech severity index</measure>
    <time_frame>day 0</time_frame>
    <description>The main objective is to demonstrate that the carcinologic speech severity index (C2SI), obtained by an automatic speech processing tool, produces equivalent or superior outcomes than a score of speech intelligibility obtained by human listeners, in terms of quality of life foreseeing the speech handicap, after the treatment of oral and/or pharyngeal cancer.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
